{
  "info": {
    "name": "QZPAY V2 \u2014 Merchant API",
    "description": "API dokumentasi merchant QZPAY V2. Khusus endpoint yang bisa diakses pake API Key.\n\n## Environment Variables\nSet environment `QZPAY_V2_PUBLIC` dengan:\n- `base_url`: `https://api.qzpayment.com/v2`\n- `qzpay_key`: API Key kamu (format: qz_...)\n- `qzpay_secret`: Isi SAMA dengan API Key (digunakan sebagai secret HMAC)\n- `merchant_id`: ID merchant kamu\n- `store_id`: ID store\n- `payment_id`: ID payment\n- `reference_id`: QZ-XXXX\n- `webhook_id`: ID webhook\n- `api_key_id`: ID API key\n- `staff_id`: ID staff\n- `notification_id`: ID notifikasi\n- `payment_link_id`: ID payment link\n- `payment_link_code`: Code payment link\n- `wd_id`: ID withdrawal\n- `payment_amount`, `wd_amount`: nominal\n\n## Auth\nSemua request (kecuali public endpoint) wajib HMAC-SHA256 signing dengan:\n- `X-QZPAY-KEY`: API Key\n- `X-QZPAY-TIMESTAMP`: ISO8601 UTC\n- `X-QZPAY-SIGNATURE`: HMAC-SHA256(METHOD:PATH:BODY_HASH:TIMESTAMP)\n\nSignature sudah auto-calculate dari Pre-request Script.\n\n## Signature Formula\n```\nbodyHash = SHA256(body) dalam lowercase hex\nstringToSign = METHOD + \":\" + PATH + \":\" + bodyHash + \":\" + timestamp\nsignature = HMAC-SHA256(stringToSign, apiKey)\n```\nUntuk GET/DELETE: body hash = SHA256(\"\") = e3b0c44298fc1c149afbf4c8996fb92427ae41e4649b934ca495991b7852b855",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
